reviewText: Nazareth has a great sense of humor!  Our entire family, 10 of us enjoy watching his show!  Keep up the good work.

I thought I would have an accident when I watched this DVD the first time...I barely made it to the bathroom. I love this type of humor and Nazareth has a great style that subtle, but hilarious!

This is perfect for a family night or a get together with friends. You won't be disapointed.
